<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Grant Writing Resources - Tips & Guides</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: 'Arial', sans-serif;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            background-color: #f9f9f9;
            color: #333;
        }

        header {
            background-color: #b7c8dc;
            color: white;
            text-align: center;
            padding: 0.5rem;
        }

        main {
            padding: 2rem;
        }

        section {
            margin-bottom: 2rem;
        }

        h1 {
            font-size: 2.5rem;
            font-weight: bold;
            color: #0056b3;
            text-shadow: 1px 1px 2px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.3);
        }

        h2, h3 {
            color: #0056b3;
        }

        ul {
            list-style-type: disc;
            margin: 0;
            padding-left: 20px;
        }

        ul li {
            margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
        }

        .guide {
            background: #ffffff;
            padding: 0.7rem;
            margin-bottom: 1rem;
            border-radius: 5px;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 8px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
            animation: fadeIn 0.5s ease-in-out;
        }

        @keyframes fadeIn {
            from {
                opacity: 0;
                transform: translateY(20px);
            }
            to {
                opacity: 1;
                transform: translateY(0);
            }
        }

        footer {
            background-color: #333;
            color: #fff;
            text-align: center;
            padding: 0.5rem;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <header>
        <h1>Grant Writing Resources</h1>
        <p>Practical Tips and Guidance for Crafting Effective Grants</p>
    </header>

    <main>
        <section class="tips">
            <h2>Grant Writing Tips</h2>
            <ul>
                <li>Understand the grant requirements.</li>
                <li>Tailor your application to the funder’s goals.</li>
                <li>Make a clear and compelling case for your project.</li>
                <li>Provide realistic and achievable budgets.</li>
                <li>Include measurable outcomes and impact.</li>
            </ul>
        </section>

        <section class="guides">
            <h2>Guides for Writing Grants</h2>
            <article class="guide">
                <h3>Guide 1: Structuring Your Grant Proposal</h3>
                <p>Learn how to structure your grant proposal effectively, including the executive summary, problem statement, goals, methods, and budget.</p>
            </article>
            <article class="guide">
                <h3>Guide 2: Tips for Crafting a Winning Budget</h3>
                <p>Understand how to create a clear and realistic budget for your project, and how to present it in a way that demonstrates your commitment to the funder’s objectives.</p>
            </article>
        </section>
    </main>

    <footer>
        <p>&copy; Pratik. All rights reserved.</p>
    </footer>
</body>
</html>
